	        Send us your pictures   ·  Send us your stories A British man was stunned to spot two amorous 3 m pythons mating while dangling in the air, within arm’s length of his kitchen window on Friday morning. Keith Williams filmed the serpents enjoying a mammoth 50 minutes of forked tongue foreplay while hanging from patio rafters outside his home in Ballina, New South Wales. He shared the video on Twitter, which he captioned: “Holy sh*t. Outside the kitchen window. I think spring is here early.”  The local councillor and dad-of-one had been making a coffee in his kitchen when he saw the randy reptiles hanging directly outside the glass. Keith has now dubbed himself an international purveyor of snake pornography. - MAGAZINE FEATURES   24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  